{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2cc6f8fdd8","title":"战斗的誓言——打倒“三害”！","origin":"《武汉大学右派言论汇编》（中共武汉大学社会主义思想教育办公室，1957.12）。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d268180a54","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":28,"articleId":"2cc6f8fdd8"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3db6e228de","name":"吴开斌"},{"id":"c504f98253","name":"武汉大学"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b36052bd2e","type":"title","text":"战斗的誓言——打倒“三害”！","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2cc6f8fdd8"},{"id":"bc6bf2d37d","type":"authors","text":"武汉大学吴开斌","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2cc6f8fdd8"},{"id":"00c7ea07ac","type":"subtitle","text":"[吴开斌：武汉大学中文系学生]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2cc6f8fdd8"},{"id":"ed31654fea","type":"paragraph","text":"“三害”在武大根深蒂固，流毒全校，师生员工深受其害，“三害”不除，群众痛苦不能解除，正气不能上升，学校不能办好，珞珈山上也不能有光明！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2cc6f8fdd8"},{"id":"ec52007d65","type":"paragraph","text":"党中央和毛主席号召要除“三害”，革命的青年应立即行动起来，投入战斗。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2cc6f8fdd8"},{"id":"f99cbdcd81","type":"paragraph","text":"我们誓与“三害”斗争到底，决不退缩，决不退缩，也决不因为某些人的冷淡而烟消火灭，偃旗息鼓。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2cc6f8fdd8"},{"id":"d4964a6280","type":"paragraph","text":"“三害”一日不除，我们一日不罢休！","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2cc6f8fdd8"},{"id":"765f763b38","type":"paragraph","text":"与“三害”誓不两立，不共戴天！","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2cc6f8fdd8"},{"id":"36841526e9","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒“三害”！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2cc6f8fdd8"}],"page":{"id":"51eea209d8","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2cc6f8fdd8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}